OL,3,CPolice called to council meeting after
OL,4,Cexplosive argument in chamber
OL,6,FThe row broke in the middle a debate
OL,7,Fon a controversial housing scheme,
OL,8,Fwhich was screened online.
OL,10,FFootage shows tensions in the meeting
OL,11,Fbuilding, with Oldham Mayor Zahid
OL,12,FChauhan calling for calm, before a
OL,13,Fnumber of councillors begin shouting
OL,14,Fat each other, and the meeting is
OL,15,Fadjourned.
OL,17,FShouts of "take that back" and "we all
OL,18,Fheard what he said" can be heard in
OL,19,Fthe chamber.
