OL,4,Cexplosive argument in chamber
OL,6,FAs Councillor Sheldon approached
OL,7,FCouncillor Quigg it is claimed both
OL,8,Fcould then be seen squaring up to each
OL,9,Fother, with Quigg seen pushing Sheldon.
OL,11,FThe two men were separated by other
OL,12,FConservative councillors surrounding
OL,13,Fthem.
OL,15,FA riot van and police cars were
OL,16,Fpictured outside the council building,
OL,17,Fwith Greater Manchester Police
OL,18,Fconfirming officers had also been
OL,19,Fcalled out during the evening to a
OL,20,Fprotest gathering outside.
