OL,3,CPolice called to council meeting after
OL,4,Cexplosive argument in chamber
OL,6,FOfficers are then believed to have
OL,7,Fbeen called over to the incident
OL,8,Finside the chamber, with the meeting
OL,9,Fremained adjourned for an hour and 45
OL,10,Fminutes, while police took statements
OL,11,Fand political groups convened in
OL,12,Fprivate rooms to discuss how to move
OL,13,Fforward.
OL,15,FThe meeting was later suspended.
OL,17,FSpeaking to ITV Granada Reports
OL,18,FCouncillor Quigg denied anything took
OL,19,Fplace during the meeting, and declined
OL,20,Fto comment any further.
